ptex
------------------------------------------
Ptex is a texture mapping system developed by Walt Disney Animation Studios for
production-quality rendering.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libPtex-devel-2.4.3-1bl1
  libPtex2.4-2.4.3-1bl1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.0-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/wdas/ptex

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/wdas/ptex/archive/refs/tags/v2.4.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ptex-2.4.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ptex-2.4.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ptex-2.4.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ptex-2.4.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libPtex2.4-2.4.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libPtex-devel-2.4.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ptex)
  /usr/bin/ptxinfo.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ptex.README
  /usr/share/doc/ptex/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/ptex/README.md

(libPtex2.4)
  /usr/bin/cygPtex-2.4.dll

(libPtex-devel)
  /usr/include/PtexExports.h
  /usr/include/PtexHalf.h
  /usr/include/PtexInt.h
  /usr/include/PtexPlatform.h
  /usr/include/PtexUtils.h
  /usr/include/PtexVersion.h
  /usr/include/Ptexture.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-exports-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/Ptex/ptex-exports.cmake
  /usr/lib/libPtex.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ptex.pc

